{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPresentTheUI","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Related Documentation","anchor":"Related-Documentation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The matching API reference for the views described here lives in the "},{"code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" documentation."}],"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/PlatformBehavior","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService"]},{"title":"How-to Guides","generated":true,"anchor":"How-to-Guides","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToAddAPermanentLicense","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPreviewAndTest"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI"},{"type":"text","text":" ships three view modifiers that wrap RevenueCatUI’s surfaces with platform-aware presentation. Each is bound to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallState"},{"type":"text","text":": presentation flags drive visibility, and the bindings dispatch matching paywall actions back through the store on dismissal. There is no local sheet state."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For platform behavior details (iOS ","type":"text"},{"code":"fullScreenCover","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" vs macOS sheet sizing, App Store deep link on macOS), see "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/PlatformBehavior","type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Before-you-start","type":"heading","text":"Before you start","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This guide assumes:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You have completed ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService","type":"reference"},{"text":". The plugin is registered and ","type":"text"},{"code":"observeCustomerInfo","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" runs on launch.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Your app target depends on the ","type":"text"},{"code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" product:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":[".product(name: \"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI\", package: \"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\"),"]},{"anchor":"Step-1-Attach-both-sheets-to-a-root-view","level":2,"text":"Step 1: Attach both sheets to a root view","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The simplest wiring uses the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"revenueCatPaywall(state:send:)"},{"type":"text","text":" modifier — one call, both sheets, both dismissals:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["import SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI","","struct RootView: View {","    @Environment(AppStore.self) private var store","","    var body: some View {","        ContentView()","            .revenueCatPaywall(state: store.paywall) { action in","                store.send(.paywall(action))","            }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The closure receives a ","type":"text"},{"code":"PaywallAction","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" ("},{"code":".dismiss","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"code":".dismissCustomerCenter","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":") and lifts it into your root action. Place the modifier on the topmost view that should host both sheets.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Step 2: Trigger the paywall from a feature","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Step-2-Trigger-the-paywall-from-a-feature"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Dispatch ","type":"text"},{"code":".request(reason:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" with a short identifier describing why you’re asking. ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallState.requestedReason"},{"type":"text","text":" stores the value so the sheet (or analytics) can tailor its copy:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["Button(\"Export PDF\") {","    store.send(.paywall(.request(reason: \"export-pdf\")))","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The plugin sets ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallState.isPresented = true"},{"text":". The ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"revenueCatPaywall"},{"type":"text","text":" modifier observes the change and presents "},{"code":"RevenueCatUI.PaywallView","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"text":"Step 3: Trigger the customer center","level":2,"anchor":"Step-3-Trigger-the-customer-center","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Existing subscribers manage their subscription through the customer center. Surface a button that dispatches ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".presentCustomerCenter"},{"text":":","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["if store.paywall.isPro {","    Button(\"Manage Subscription\") {","        store.send(.paywall(.presentCustomerCenter))","    }","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"code":"revenueCatCustomerCenter","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" modifier presents ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RevenueCatUI.CustomerCenterView"},{"text":" on iOS. On macOS it opens the system App Store subscriptions URL and immediately fires ","type":"text"},{"code":"onDismiss","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" (RevenueCatUI does not ship a customer center on macOS — see ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/PlatformBehavior","type":"reference"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Step 4: Manual wiring (optional)","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Step-4-Manual-wiring-optional"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you need only one sheet, or you want to interleave other modifiers between them, attach the primitive modifiers directly. Each takes a real ","type":"text"},{"code":"Binding<Bool>","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"; build it with a ","type":"text"},{"code":"set:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" that dispatches the matching dismiss action when SwiftUI clears the flag:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["ContentView()","    .revenueCatPaywall(","        isPresented: Binding(","            get: { store.paywall.isPresented },","            set: { if !$0 { store.send(.paywall(.dismiss)) } }","        )","    )","    .revenueCatCustomerCenter(","        isPresented: Binding(","            get: { store.paywall.isCustomerCenterPresented },","            set: { if !$0 { store.send(.paywall(.dismissCustomerCenter)) } }","        )","    )"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The convenience modifier ","type":"text"},{"code":"revenueCatPaywall(state:send:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is exactly equivalent to this wiring.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Step 5: Restore from inside the paywall","level":2,"anchor":"Step-5-Restore-from-inside-the-paywall","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"RevenueCatUI’s ","type":"text"},{"code":"PaywallView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" provides its own restore button by default. If you need an additional restore affordance elsewhere (a Settings row, for example), dispatch ","type":"text"},{"code":".restorePurchases","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":":"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["Button(\"Restore Purchases\") {","    store.send(.paywall(.restorePurchases))","}",".disabled(store.paywall.isLoading)"]},{"text":"What happens on dismiss","level":2,"anchor":"What-happens-on-dismiss","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the user dismisses the paywall, the plugin’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".dismiss"},{"text":" action clears ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallState.isPresented"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"requestedReason"},{"text":", then dispatches ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".refreshCustomerInfo"},{"text":" so the gate is reconciled — the user may have purchased while the sheet was open.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the user dismisses the customer center, the plugin’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".dismissCustomerCenter"},{"text":" action clears ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isCustomerCenterPresented"},{"text":". No refresh is dispatched, since opening the customer center does not change entitlement state by itself; the live ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"customerInfoStream"},{"text":" from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Step 5"},{"text":" of ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService"},{"type":"text","text":" picks up any subscription change RevenueCat reports asynchronously."}]}]}],"sections":[],"kind":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Attach the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"revenueCatPaywall"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"revenueCatCustomerCenter"},{"type":"text","text":" 